message: Combine two animals, ideally a large one from land and one from water, to create an amphibious hybrid. Always use the mutation catalyst twice on the combined item; the first mutation often gives a negative score, but the second will turn it into a valuable 'super-mutant.' For growth serum, you can either grow a large animal before combining or use it on your 'super-mutant' after mutations. Applying growth serum to a super-mutant item where one component isn't yet 'grown' often yields a significant value increase. Be cautious with multiple growth serums on already grown components as it can sometimes decrease value. Aim for values around 60-65.

Crucially, apply the 'mutation catalyst' *twice* to this combined item. The first mutation often results in a negative score, but the second mutation will transform it into a high-value 'super-mutant'. Avoid combining more than two animals, as this can lead to 'overcomplicated' negative values.

Do not combine more than two animals, and submit after the second mutation.
